<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SangreVital - Dashboard</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <!-- Google Fonts - Montserrat -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --sangre-primary: #dc3545;
            --sangre-secondary: #f8d7da;
            --sangre-dark: #c82333;
            --sangre-light: #f8f9fa;
            --sangre-card-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #fefefe;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .navbar-sangre {
            background-color: var(--sangre-primary) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3);
            padding: 0.8rem 0;
        }
        
        .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .hero-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.95) 0%, rgba(200, 35, 51, 0.9) 100%), 
                        url('https://d100mj7v0l85u5.cloudfront.net/s3fs-public/2022-08/donacion-de-sangre.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--sangre-card-shadow);
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .hero-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 70%);
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        .profile-card {
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--sangre-card-shadow);
            border: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            background: white;
        }
        
        .profile-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.15);
        }
        
        .blood-badge {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            color: var(--sangre-primary);
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.2);
        }
        
        .stats-card {
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: var(--sangre-card-shadow);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--sangre-primary);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .stats-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .btn-sangre {
            background-color: var(--sangre-primary);
            color: white;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-sangre:hover {
            background-color: var(--sangre-dark);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn-sangre-outline {
            border: 2px solid var(--sangre-primary);
            color: var(--sangre-primary);
            background: transparent;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .btn-sangre-outline:hover {
            background-color: var(--sangre-primary);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: var(--sangre-primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        
        .donation-progress {
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background: #f0f0f0;
        }
        
        .progress-bar {
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        
        .nav-pills .nav-link.active {
            background-color: var(--sangre-primary);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.4);
        }
        
        .nav-pills .nav-link {
            color: var(--sangre-primary);
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--sangre-card-shadow);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.15);
        }
        
        .card-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--sangre-primary);
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .card-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--sangre-primary);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        
        .reward-item {
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
        }
        
        .reward-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.15);
            border-color: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.2);
        }
        
        .alert-custom {
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.08);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--sangre-primary);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #000 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        
        footer h5 {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        footer h5::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -8px;
            left: 0;
            width: 40px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--sangre-primary);
        }
        
        .profile-avatar {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--sangre-primary);
            border: 3px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.2);
        }
        
        .section-divider {
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--sangre-primary) 0%, rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1) 100%);
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #eee;
        }
        
        .info-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .info-icon {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--sangre-primary);
        }
        
        /* Animaciones */
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        
        .pulse-animation {
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        
        /* Ajustes específicos para Montserrat */
        .lead {
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        }
        
        .small, small {
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 0.1px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }
        
        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-card {
                padding: 2rem 1rem;
            }
            
            .hero-card h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .profile-avatar {
                width: 90px;
                height: 90px;
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark navbar-sangre sticky-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/dashboard">
                <img src="/images/logo2.png" alt=""  width="40"> SangreVital
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="/dashboard"><i class="bi bi-house-door me-1"></i> Inicio</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/donation-centers"><i class="bi bi-hospital me-1"></i> Centros</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/appointments"><i class="bi bi-calendar-check me-1"></i> Mis Citas</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/rewards"><i class="bi bi-award me-1"></i> Recompensas</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <div class="dropdown">
                        <a href="#" class="d-flex align-items-center text-white text-decoration-none dropdown-toggle" id="dropdownUser" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                            <div class="me-2 d-none d-sm-block">
                                <div class="small">Bienvenido</div>
                                <div class="fw-semibold"><%= donor.first_name || 'Donante' %></div>
                            </div>
                            <i class="bi bi-person-circle fs-4"></i>
                        </a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end shadow" aria-labelledby="dropdownUser">
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/profile"><i class="bi bi-person me-2"></i> Mi perfil</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/settings"><i class="bi bi-gear me-2"></i> Configuración</a></li>
                            <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item text-danger" href="/logout"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right me-2"></i> Cerrar sesión</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container py-4">
        <!-- Hero Welcome Card -->
        <div class="hero-card text-center">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">¡Bienvenido, Héroe!</h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4">Gracias por ser parte de nuestra comunidad de donantes. Cada donación puede salvar hasta 3 vidas.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-center align-items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="badge blood-badge">
                            <i class="bi bi-droplet me-1"></i> Grupo <%= donor.blood_type %>
                        </span>
                        <a href="/schedule-appointment" class="btn btn-light btn-lg pulse-animation">
                            <i class="bi bi-calendar-plus me-2"></i> Agendar Donación
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <!-- Profile Column -->
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="profile-card p-4 h-100">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="profile-avatar">
                            <i class="bi bi-person-heart"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mb-1"><%= donor.first_name %> <%= donor.last_name %></h3>
                        <p class="text-muted small">Donante desde <%= donor.registration_date || 'N/A' %></p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                    
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>Información Personal</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li class="info-item">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <span class="info-icon">
                                    <i class="bi bi-envelope"></i>
                                </span>
                                <span><%= donor.email || 'No disponible' %></span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="info-item">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <span class="info-icon">
                                    <i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i>
                                </span>
                                <span><%= donor.address || 'No disponible' %></span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="info-item">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <span class="info-icon">
                                    <i class="bi bi-calendar"></i>
                                </span>
                                <span>
                                    <% 
                                        function formatDate(dateStr) {
                                            if (!dateStr) return 'No disponible';
                                            const d = new Date(dateStr);
                                            if (isNaN(d)) return 'No disponible';
                                            const day = String(d.getDate()).padStart(2, '0');
                                            const month = String(d.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0');
                                            const year = d.getFullYear();
                                            return `${day}/${month}/${year}`;
                                        }
                                    %>
                                    <%= formatDate(donor.birth_date) %>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                    
                    <a href="/edit-profile" class="btn btn-sangre w-100">
                        <i class="bi bi-pencil-square me-2"></i> Editar Perfil
                    </a>
                    <a href="/health-questionnaire" class="btn btn-sangre w-100 mt-3">
                      <i class="bi bi-clipboard-pulse me-2"></i> Cuestionario de Salud
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Main Content Column -->
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <!-- Stats Row -->
                <div class="row mb-4 g-3">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="stats-card p-3 h-100">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                <div class="feature-icon" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; font-size: 1.5rem;">
                                    <i class="bi bi-droplet"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h6 class="text-muted mb-0 ms-2">DONACIONES</h6>
                            </div>
                            <h2 class="fw-bold text-danger"><%= donor.donations_count || 0 %></h2>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-muted small">Vidas salvadas: <strong class="text-danger"><%= (donor.donations_count || 0) * 3 %></strong></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="stats-card p-3 h-100">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                <div class="feature-icon" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; font-size: 1.5rem;">
                                    <i class="bi bi-clock-history"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h6 class="text-muted mb-0 ms-2">PRÓXIMA DONACIÓN</h6>
                            </div>
                            <h2 class="fw-bold text-danger"><%= donor.next_donation_days || 'N/A' %></h2>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-muted small">Disponible el <%= donor.next_donation_date || 'N/A' %></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="stats-card p-3 h-100">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                <div class="feature-icon" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; font-size: 1.5rem;">
                                    <i class="bi bi-star"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h6 class="text-muted mb-0 ms-2">PUNTOS</h6>
                            </div>
                            <h2 class="fw-bold text-danger"><%= donor.points || 0 %></h2>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-muted small">Canjeables por recompensas</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Next Donation Card -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-0"><i class="bi bi-calendar-check me-2"></i>Próxima Cita</h5>
                            <span class="badge bg-danger bg-opacity-10 text-danger">Confirmada</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="row align-items-center">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                                    <div class="feature-icon me-3" style="width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 1.2rem;">
                                        <i class="bi bi-hospital"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h6 class="mb-0"><strong><%= donor.next_appointment_center || 'No disponible' %></strong></h6>
                                        <small class="text-muted"><%= donor.next_appointment_address || 'No disponible' %></small>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <div class="feature-icon me-3" style="width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 1.2rem;">
                                        <i class="bi bi-clock"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h6 class="mb-0"><%= donor.next_appointment_time || 'No disponible' %></h6>
                                        <small class="text-muted">Duración aproximada: 45 min</small>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end mt-3 mt-md-0">
                                <button class="btn btn-sangre-outline me-2">Cancelar</button>
                                <button class="btn btn-sangre">Recordatorio</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Donation Progress -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-graph-up me-2"></i>Tu Progreso Anual</h5>
                        
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-1">
                                <span class="small fw-semibold">Donaciones este año</span>
                                <span class="small fw-semibold"><%= donor.donations_this_year || 0 %> de 4</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="progress donation-progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar bg-danger" role="progressbar" style="width:<%= ((donor.donations_this_year || 0) / 4) * 100 %>%">
                                    <div class="progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated" style="width:100%"></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="alert alert-custom">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill fs-4 me-3 text-danger"></i>
                                <div>
                                    <strong>¡Faltan <%= (4-(donor.donations_this_year || 0)) %> donaciones!</strong> 
                                    <div class="small">Completa tu meta anual y recibe puntos extra.</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Rewards Section -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                            <h5 class="card-title mb-0"><i class="bi bi-award me-2"></i>Tus Recompensas</h5>
                            <a href="/rewards" class="text-danger fw-semibold">Ver todas <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></a>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="row g-3">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="reward-item p-3 text-center h-100">
                                    <div class="feature-icon mx-auto">
                                        <i class="bi bi-cup-straw"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-semibold">Café Gratis</h6>
                                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3">200 puntos</p>
                                    <button class="btn btn-sangre btn-sm w-100">Canjear</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="reward-item p-3 text-center h-100">
                                    <div class="feature-icon mx-auto">
                                        <i class="bi bi-ticket-perforated"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-semibold">Entrada Cine</h6>
                                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3">350 puntos</p>
                                    <button class="btn btn-sangre btn-sm w-100">Canjear</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="reward-item p-3 text-center h-100">
                                    <div class="feature-icon mx-auto">
                                        <i class="bi bi-bag"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-semibold">Descuento 20%</h6>
                                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3">150 puntos</p>
                                    <button class="btn btn-sangre btn-sm w-100">Canjear</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-droplet-fill text-danger me-2"></i> SangreVital</h5>
                    <p class="small mt-3">Conectando donantes con quienes más lo necesitan desde 2025. Cada gota cuenta en nuestra misión por salvar vidas.</p>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <a href="#" class="text-white me-3"><i class="bi bi-facebook fs-5"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="text-white me-3"><i class="bi bi-twitter fs-5"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="text-white me-3"><i class="bi bi-instagram fs-5"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-4">
                    <h5>Enlaces</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled small mt-3">
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="#" class="text-white text-decoration-none">Centros de donación</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="#" class="text-white text-decoration-none">Requisitos</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="#" class="text-white text-decoration-none">Beneficios</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="#" class="text-white text-decoration-none">Preguntas frecuentes</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
                    <h5>Contacto</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled small mt-3">
